{"tid":842402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國1名男子天生只有睪丸沒有陰莖，好不容易動手術裝上假陰莖後與女友翻雲覆雨一夜，卻在人生的第一次體驗高潮後，昏迷了5天","createTime":"2018-09-30T09:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T10:19:32.000Z","uid":205996,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a3ba3d836cb9a451bfb47e2ff235fa7d2523ae5d","tid":842402,"uid":205996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:38:19.000Z","msg":"英國1名男子天生只有睪丸沒有陰莖，好不容易動手術裝上假陰莖後與女友翻雲覆雨一夜，卻在人生的第一次體驗高潮後，昏迷了5天，差一點就要升天。<br />\n<br />\n英國45歲的男子沃德爾（Andrew Wardle）因為「膀胱外翻」，導致他的生殖器發育不完整，出現了只有睪丸沒有陰莖的。今年6月22日，他耗資5萬英鎊（約新台幣200萬)，裝好了仿生陰莖，他更稱其尺寸荒謬的大，女友都十分滿意。<br />\n<br />\n迫不急待的他本月初與交往6年的女友費比恩（Fedra Fabian）共享初夜，他還對媒體表示：「高潮的體驗真是美好。」<br />\n<br />\n沒想到沃德爾開始有嘔吐、發燒等症狀，他們原已為是諾羅病毒。過了數日以後，沃德爾原要去錄節目後，卻忽然昏倒，只好趕緊將他送醫治療，沃德爾卻昏迷了整整5天，恐怕高潮真的要讓他「升天」了。<br />\n<br />\n女友表示這真是太可怕了，擔心是造成的傷害是由性行為造成的。 還好醫院發現這是一個膽囊問題，做手術後就無大礙。沃德爾表示，經過這次經驗他仍不畏懼，會繼續享受床笫之歡，也希望將來能有自己的小孩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180930000819-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180930000819-260408&d=2Ke6KMOVqt42n74fogkwYUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=cece508a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180930000819-260408</a>"},{"pid":"bd8c369d4b65b5924395c0d20c787232d1ec3d71","tid":842402,"uid":4525,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:39:55.000Z","msg":"爽死了"},{"pid":"ff37c7d52d9169b12e21c182891433bc4a0c4b53","tid":842402,"uid":75137,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />假J都有高潮？"},{"pid":"6686a1bd36dc2cd30fa4925040f058bd604ee1f4","tid":842402,"uid":49918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:42:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e8aa98890a69a0b026fe24caadfbb9215366b83","tid":842402,"uid":170159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:47:55.000Z","msg":"駁咗神經所以有高潮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82631c33b4cfdf149868ab3968a93eefaad14a9","tid":842402,"uid":187932,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T10:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/180605_a9c50b4c23e6439de7af23d628bafd05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F180605_a9c50b4c23e6439de7af23d628bafd05.jpg&h=1346864d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8cafdc0d8196c049db0eb433cbf331f219e2d99","tid":842402,"uid":187932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/180817_809261febc5c87cc4149134766aa3efb.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F180817_809261febc5c87cc4149134766aa3efb.jpeg&h=41689614&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb55859169f8b2537e4445fa280a534538ca7cb2","tid":842402,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T10:08:43.000Z","msg":"Titlegore"},{"pid":"13e538b94734cc54d8c4d2631b548c368fe83309","tid":842402,"uid":52943,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T10:13:29.000Z","msg":"佢得條假鳩都叫做過愛<br />\n有幾多連登仔擁有一條完整賓州但係連波皮都未掂過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59362430501f55a9df18a0119acd1eb7a43bde20","tid":842402,"uid":45120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T10:19:32.000Z","msg":"冇jer都keep到6年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}